        <h1>Remedies for dryhair</h1>
        <h2>Regular oiling with hot oil </h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Hot hair oil massage is one of the essential treatments for dry hair. Various oils are useful to treat dry hair effectively, such as coconut oil, almond oil, jojoba oil, and olive oil. 
            All these oils are rich in vitamin E and antioxidants that help lock the moisture in your hair.
             You can combine all these oils to make an effective homemade oil. </p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Mix all oils and warm it but do not boil.</li>
            <li>Gently massage this oil on the scalp and hair.</li> 
            <li>Cover the hair with a warm towel.</li>
            <li>Leave for 30 to 45 minutes or overnight.</li>
            <li>After this time, shampoo and rinse the hair.</li>
        </ol>
            </div>
