        <h2>Egg yolk and water pack </h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>Eggs are rich in proteins, sulfur, biotin, and honey is rich in antioxidants. Both ingredients help restore the moisture to avoid further damage.  </p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Separate the egg yolk from the egg white.</li>
            <li>Then add 3 tablespoons of water in it and mix well.</li>
            <li>Apply all over your hair and wait for 30 minutes before washing with cold water.</li>
        </ol>
            </div>
