        <h2>Yogurt and honey mask</h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>This combination is excellent for dry hair. Yoghurt is rich in proteins that build hair, has lactic acid that cleanses the scalp.
             The honey helps to seal the moisture and prevent damage.  </p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Combine yoghurt and honey nicely.</li>
            <li>Apply the mask onto your scalp and hair.</li>
            <li>Leave it for 15 -20 minutes.</li>
            <li>Rinse your hair with cold water and shampoo.</li>
        </ol>   
            </div>
