        <h2> Avocado and banana pack </h2>
        <div class="xyz">
            <div class="pqr">
        <p>It is the most trending hair pack now. Avocado is rich in proteins, amino acids, and vitamins to soothe the scalp and promote healthy hair growth. 
            It contains natural oils that moisturize your hair. Banana contains folic acid and potassium that nourishes the hair.</p>
        <p>How to apply this?</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Blend avocado and peeled banana in a fine paste.</li> 
            <li>Add some drops of olive oil and blend it again.</li> 
            <li>Apply this mask to your hair and cover it with a shower cap.</li>
            <li>Leave it for 20-30 minutes and rinse it off.</li>
        </ol>
            </div>
