        <h2> Rice milk and honey hair wash </h2>
            <div class="xyz">
                <div class="pqr">
            <p>Rice milk is one of the old but famous tricks to seal the natural moisture in your hair. It also nourishes the hair.
                 Honey is a natural emollient that keeps your hair smooth.</p>
            <p>How to apply this?</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Take one cup of rice milk and add 2 tablespoons of honey in it.</li>
                <li>Mix the ingredients until it is consistent.</li>
                <li>Apply this mixture over your hair and allow it to sit for 10-15 minutes.</li>
                <li>Wash it off with shampoo. </li>
            </ol>
